### Test Trip Feed
GET http://localhost:5001/api/trips


### Create a Test User
POST http://localhost:5001/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "googleId": "test-google-id-123",
  "name": "Satyam (Test Account)",
  "phone": "9876543210",
  "bio": "Minimalist designer and full-stack engineer building TripMate."
}


### Google OAuth Login  (replace token with a real Google idToken from the frontend)
POST http://localhost:5001/api/auth/google
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idToken": "PASTE_REAL_GOOGLE_ID_TOKEN_HERE"
}